#---------------------------------KEY CODES------------------------------------#
|														                                       					   |
|		KEY				            |			CODE		 |		        	ACTION			           |
|																	                                       		   |
|		e ......................... 14 .................... Zoom In			           |
|		q ......................... 12 .................... Zoom Out		           |
|		w ......................... 13 .................... Scale UP		           |
|		s ......................... 1 ..................... Scale DOWN		         |
|		arrow left ................ 123 ................... Move map LEFT	         |
|		arrow right ............... 124 ................... Move map RIGHT 	       |
|		arrow down ................ 125 ................... Move map DOWN	         |
|		arrow up .................. 126 ................... Move map UP		         |
|		ESC ....................... 53 .................... EXIT		    	         |
|															                                      				   |
